00:12:45.000 --> 00:12:46.350
para sa isang napakahalagang gawain,

00:12:47.040 --> 00:12:48.830
hindi ba dapat may presyo?

00:12:51.390 --> 00:12:52.950
Mayroon kang ilang lakas ng loob.

00:12:55.600 --> 00:12:56.550
Mga duwag

00:12:57.350 --> 00:12:59.480
Hindi ako mangangahas na magtrabaho para sa iyo, ginoo.

00:13:02.040 --> 00:13:03.040
Kapag ito ay tapos na,

00:13:03.480 --> 00:13:04.950
ang buong pamilya mo ay makakalaya sa pagkaalipin.

00:13:07.790 --> 00:13:08.760
Salamat po, Mr. Chairman.

00:13:18.320 --> 00:13:18.880
Tagapangulo,

00:13:19.230 --> 00:13:20.270
ang taong ito ay hindi maaaring panatilihin sa paligid.

00:13:21.000 --> 00:13:22.070
Hindi mo kailangang sabihin sa akin.

00:13:24.270 --> 00:13:25.230
Anumang balita

00:13:25.230 --> 00:13:26.480
mula sa Mansion ng Panginoon?

00:13:27.000 --> 00:13:28.880
Bihira na siyang makita lately.

00:13:29.200 --> 00:13:30.740
Ngunit ang kanyang anak na si Wen Jue

00:13:31.240 --> 00:13:32.760
nakitang gumagawa ng eksena

00:13:32.760 --> 00:13:33.640
sa gate ng Ma Gang kaninang umaga.

00:13:35.830 --> 00:13:37.800
Ang matandang soro na si Wen Yu

00:13:39.240 --> 00:13:41.680
ay batid na ang aming samahan ay nagkakaroon ng katanyagan.

00:13:42.470 --> 00:13:43.560
Nagsisimula na siyang matakot sa amin,

00:13:43.950 --> 00:13:46.000
o alam niyang nauubos na ang oras niya.

00:13:47.470 --> 00:13:48.950
Kaya, gusto niyang humanap ng backer para sa kanyang anak.

00:13:51.390 --> 00:13:53.240
Tila ang mga alingawngaw sa paligid ng bayan

00:13:54.030 --> 00:13:55.760
hawakan ang ilang katotohanan.

00:13:57.830 --> 00:13:58.360
Tagapangulo,

00:13:58.710 --> 00:14:00.880
paano kung magsanib pwersa ang dalawang gang na yan?

00:14:06.030 --> 00:14:07.640
Sabihin sa aming mga lalaki

00:14:08.360 --> 00:14:09.880
para manatiling low profile sa ngayon.

00:14:11.240 --> 00:14:13.470
Hanggang sa maalis ko na ang matandang tanga

00:14:15.070 --> 00:14:16.830
at tiyakin ang aking posisyon bilang Chairman,

00:14:17.360 --> 00:14:19.470
magbabayad sila ng isang daang beses

00:14:20.830 --> 00:14:23.030
ang kinuha nila sa akin.

00:14:30.760 --> 00:14:31.270
Miss,

00:14:31.270 --> 00:14:33.070
pumayag ba si Xubu Huai na putulin ang pakikipag-ugnayan?

00:14:33.560 --> 00:14:34.510
Pinag-isipan ko na.

00:14:34.880 --> 00:14:37.070
Ang pagtanggal ng pakikipag-ugnayan ay hindi nakadepende sa iba,

00:14:37.360 --> 00:14:38.360
dapat ako ang bahala.

00:14:38.590 --> 00:14:40.120
Ang dahilan kung bakit ako gustong pakasalan ng aking ama

00:14:40.390 --> 00:14:41.800
ay ang kanyang sakit.

00:14:41.800 --> 00:14:42.910
Ngunit, ano ang kailangang gawin nito

00:14:42.950 --> 00:14:44.680
sa kasal mo?

00:14:44.680 --> 00:14:46.030
Isipin mo,

00:14:47.390 --> 00:14:49.360
nag-aalala siya na baka may mangyari sa kanya

00:14:49.440 --> 00:14:50.640
at maiiwan akong mag-isa.

00:14:51.560 --> 00:14:52.950
Kung mapapagaling ang kanyang karamdaman,

00:14:53.030 --> 00:14:55.030
at naglalaro ako ng sympathy card ng ilang beses,

00:14:55.440 --> 00:14:56.240
hindi ako naniniwala

00:14:56.240 --> 00:14:57.640
may puso siyang magpakasal

00:14:57.640 --> 00:14:58.360
kanyang mahal na anak na babae.

00:14:58.950 --> 00:14:59.880
talaga,

00:14:59.880 --> 00:15:00.680
pero Miss,

00:15:00.800 --> 00:15:01.470
Malapit na akong manalo.

00:15:11.910 --> 00:15:12.680
nanalo ako.

00:15:12.680 --> 00:15:13.760
Matalino ka talaga,

00:15:13.760 --> 00:15:14.640
at nanalo ulit.

00:15:17.460 --> 00:15:20.500
[Qinya House]

00:15:54.200 --> 00:15:55.640
Magpatingin ka ba sa doktor, Miss?

00:15:56.590 --> 00:15:57.680
Ako ang doktor dito.

00:15:58.330 --> 00:15:58.650
Umupo ka na.

00:16:02.590 --> 00:16:03.520
Batang bayani,

00:16:03.590 --> 00:16:04.830
sa huling pagkakataon na nakita kita,

00:16:04.830 --> 00:16:06.510
suot mo pa rin yang Chi You mask

00:16:06.560 --> 00:16:08.800
at panloloko ng pagkain at inumin sa pasukan ng Chunyun House.

00:16:09.270 --> 00:16:10.640
Paano ba naman isang araw lang ang pagitan

00:16:10.830 --> 00:16:12.000
at ganap kang nagbago

00:16:12.070 --> 00:16:15.150
mula sa isang street performer hanggang sa isang milagrong manggagamot?

00:16:17.390 --> 00:16:19.710
Hindi ko akalain na mag-iiwan ako ng ganoong pangmatagalang impresyon sa iyo,

00:16:20.360 --> 00:16:22.760
pagkatapos lamang ng isang maikling pagpupulong.

00:16:23.510 --> 00:16:24.320
Pwede ba

00:16:24.320 --> 00:16:26.070
na kinikilig ka sa akin?

00:16:29.240 --> 00:16:30.240
Sa account,

00:16:30.360 --> 00:16:31.880
next time you go out, young hero,

00:16:31.880 --> 00:16:33.830
maybe leave that Chi You mask at home.

00:16:35.200 --> 00:16:35.760
Why,

00:16:36.880 --> 00:16:38.620
are you scared of this mask

00:16:38.640 --> 00:16:39.390
covering my

00:16:39.390 --> 00:16:40.470
handsome face?

00:16:41.200 --> 00:16:42.390
Me saying, young hero,

00:16:43.150 --> 00:16:45.070
your skin is as thick as city walls,

00:16:45.590 --> 00:16:47.000
and the mask is not necessary.

00:16:53.240 --> 00:16:54.640
Looks like the lady here is feeling shy.

00:16:54.640 --> 00:16:55.440
True.

00:16:55.880 --> 00:16:58.320
It's quite embarrassing

00:16:58.360 --> 00:16:59.590
to expose someone's affection in public.

00:17:00.200 --> 00:17:01.270
But I, Gu Tian...

00:17:01.270 --> 00:17:03.030
Quit flattering yourself, won't you.

00:17:04.640 --> 00:17:06.320
Since when have you been become a physician?

00:17:06.760 --> 00:17:07.360
Physician Fu!

00:17:10.240 --> 00:17:11.560
Do you have to come back now?

00:17:19.470 --> 00:17:20.200
Miss,

00:17:20.470 --> 00:17:21.070
please sit down,

00:17:21.070 --> 00:17:22.070
I'll check your pulse.

00:17:22.390 --> 00:17:23.240
Physician,

00:17:23.390 --> 00:17:24.120
I'm not sick.

00:17:24.590 --> 00:17:26.150
It's my brother who insisted I come.

00:17:27.200 --> 00:17:27.800
Miss,

00:17:28.440 --> 00:17:29.390
if you don't treat an illness,

00:17:29.390 --> 00:17:30.240
it could lead to endless troubles.

00:17:45.910 --> 00:17:46.840
How is my sister doing?

00:17:47.550 --> 00:17:48.790
Her pulse is steady,

00:17:49.270 --> 00:17:50.360
muscles and veins strong,

00:17:50.880 --> 00:17:52.760
except a bit physically weak

00:17:52.840 --> 00:17:54.360
she has no other symptoms.

00:17:54.880 --> 00:17:56.000
So, that means,

00:17:56.240 --> 00:17:57.080
she's not sick.

00:17:57.790 --> 00:17:58.880
But that doesn't make sense.

00:17:59.240 --> 00:18:00.360
I think the lady

00:18:00.510 --> 00:18:02.240
must be suffering from sleeplessness and frequent dreams.

00:18:03.080 --> 00:18:04.880
That's why you look so haggard.

00:18:05.270 --> 00:18:06.150
There should be symptoms.

00:18:06.390 --> 00:18:08.360
I've already told you, I'm not sick.

00:18:09.000 --> 00:18:10.550
It's just too many trifles,

00:18:10.670 --> 00:18:11.550
keeping me up at night.

00:18:13.480 --> 00:18:15.000
Then there must be some mistake.

00:18:16.000 --> 00:18:17.240
Thank you for your time, Physician Fu.

00:18:20.270 --> 00:18:22.390
What do you mean, Physician Fu?

00:18:24.390 --> 00:18:25.510
Given Hulu's effort,

00:18:25.640 --> 00:18:27.150
we can't just wrap this up hastily.

00:18:27.480 --> 00:18:28.640
How about this, Miss?

00:18:28.960 --> 00:18:30.150
Answer a few more questions for me.

00:18:31.430 --> 00:18:32.240
Please.

00:18:33.360 --> 00:18:35.880
Where is your ancestral home?

00:18:36.030 --> 00:18:37.190
Fuchun, Wu Commandery.

00:18:37.640 --> 00:18:39.360
Jiangnan is known for its beauties.

00:18:40.080 --> 00:18:42.120
No wonder you are so beautiful.

00:18:48.080 --> 00:18:50.080
Do you remember when you came to Xichuan?

00:18:50.480 --> 00:18:52.600
In the first year of Yongshou, on the seventh day of the ninth month.

00:18:52.640 --> 00:18:54.080
The seventh day of the ninth month,

00:18:54.550 --> 00:18:56.240
which was thirteen years ago.

00:18:56.240 --> 00:18:58.080
You must be six or seven years old then.

00:18:58.550 --> 00:18:59.360
Five years old.

00:18:59.880 --> 00:19:00.670
Five years old?

00:19:01.190 --> 00:19:01.960
After you arrived, Miss,

00:19:01.960 --> 00:19:03.760
what was the first meal you had?

00:19:04.480 --> 00:19:05.670
How could she remember that?

00:19:06.270 --> 00:19:08.190
It was flatbread, sheep's milk,

00:19:08.360 --> 00:19:09.640
and some fruits.

00:19:09.880 --> 00:19:10.840
What fruits?

00:19:11.030 --> 00:19:13.080
Grapes, pomegranates, melons.

00:19:13.190 --> 00:19:14.390
How many grapes did you eat?

00:19:14.880 --> 00:19:15.670
Six.

00:19:16.150 --> 00:19:17.190
How many seeds did you spit out?

00:19:17.390 --> 00:19:18.190
Fifteen.

00:19:23.960 --> 00:19:24.480
ako...

00:19:26.030 --> 00:19:26.600
Miss,

00:19:27.310 --> 00:19:28.030
you are sick.

00:19:32.270 --> 00:19:33.310
What kind of sickness is that?

00:19:33.880 --> 00:19:36.360
I once read in my master's medical book,

00:19:36.600 --> 00:19:38.390
this illness is called 'Hyperthymesia'.

00:19:38.880 --> 00:19:41.000
It's when memories are too complex,

00:19:41.000 --> 00:19:42.360
making some hard to forget,

00:19:42.640 --> 00:19:44.000
thus causing sleepless nights.

00:19:44.670 --> 00:19:45.840
Can this disease be cured?

00:19:46.670 --> 00:19:48.390
Now that we've known the cause, it's easier to deal with.

00:19:48.390 --> 00:19:50.030
The prescriptions are readily available.

00:19:50.030 --> 00:19:50.960
Here's what we'll do, Miss.

00:19:51.360 --> 00:19:52.880
I'll prescribe some sedatives for you,

00:19:52.880 --> 00:19:54.880
and add some acupuncture therapy.

00:19:55.080 --> 00:19:55.760
You'll definitely recover.

00:19:56.190 --> 00:19:56.880
Then,

00:19:57.550 --> 00:19:58.360
about the consultation fee...

00:19:58.670 --> 00:19:59.720
Forget the fee,

00:20:00.430 --> 00:20:01.600
just treat us to a meal.

00:20:02.600 --> 00:20:04.240
We can even skip the meal.

00:20:04.790 --> 00:20:06.880
This disease is quite rare,

00:20:07.080 --> 00:20:08.670
I'd like to see if the medicine works.

00:20:09.640 --> 00:20:10.550
That's not right,

00:20:11.080 --> 00:20:13.190
how can I have Physician Fu work for free?

00:20:13.360 --> 00:20:14.190
I've got an idea.

00:20:14.600 --> 00:20:16.190
You're looking for Song Jingye, right?

00:20:16.190 --> 00:20:17.000
I'll help you with that.

00:20:18.760 --> 00:20:19.880
Didn't you say

00:20:20.030 --> 00:20:21.240
he's hard to approach?

00:20:22.270 --> 00:20:23.600
I have a way.

00:20:24.310 --> 00:20:25.760
Lagi niyang binubully ang kapatid ko,

00:20:26.430 --> 00:20:27.510
kaya hahanap ako ng pagkakataon

00:20:27.640 --> 00:20:28.600
para turuan siya ng leksyon.

00:20:34.020 --> 00:20:39.540
[Chunyun House]

00:20:41.150 --> 00:20:42.640
Nandito na tayo, Chunyun House.

00:20:43.080 --> 00:20:45.030
Kung hindi nagsisinungaling si Hulu,

00:20:45.390 --> 00:20:47.270
Darating si Song Jingye ngayon.

00:20:49.130 --> 00:20:50.240
Ang lugar na ito...

00:20:52.430 --> 00:20:53.270
Hindi ka pa nakapunta dito?

00:20:54.430 --> 00:20:55.550
Well, mayroon akong,

00:20:56.150 --> 00:20:57.840
pero para lang ayusin ang accounts ng tatay ko.

00:20:59.640 --> 00:21:01.840
Ngayon, ang iyong kuya dito ay magpapakita sa iyo sa paligid.

00:21:04.000 --> 00:21:05.030
Papasok lang tayo ng ganito?

00:21:06.270 --> 00:21:07.360
Sumunod ka sa akin at magiging maayos ka.

00:21:07.880 --> 00:21:08.880
Parang pag-uwi

00:21:09.240 --> 00:21:10.670
para nandito ako.

00:21:28.240 --> 00:21:29.120
sir,

00:21:29.120 --> 00:21:30.600
ito ba ang unang pagkakataon mo sa Xichuan?

00:21:31.190 --> 00:21:32.670
Ang lugar na ito ay itinayo ng mga manggagawa

00:21:32.670 --> 00:21:35.270
galing kay Daqin na inupahan ng amo namin.

00:21:35.360 --> 00:21:36.190
Confident ako dun

00:21:36.190 --> 00:21:37.880
ito ay isa sa mga uri sa buong mundo.

00:21:38.270 --> 00:21:39.270
Interesting.

00:21:39.790 --> 00:21:40.760
Ang aming Chunyun House,

00:21:40.880 --> 00:21:43.600
umaakit sa mga opisyal, mayayaman, at mga ginoo.

00:21:43.960 --> 00:21:45.030
Ang laki nito,

00:21:45.030 --> 00:21:47.080
tiyak na hindi mapapantayan ng mga ordinaryong lugar.

00:21:47.190 --> 00:21:48.000
natural,

00:21:48.390 --> 00:21:49.760
ang presyo dito...

00:21:50.240 --> 00:21:52.240
ay hindi isang bagay na makikita mo kahit saan.

00:21:53.190 --> 00:21:53.960
Wala na kaming pera.

00:21:55.550 --> 00:21:57.960
Ang pag-iwas sa iba ay ang pinakamahusay na ginagawa natin.

00:22:01.190 --> 00:22:02.120
Babae,

00:22:02.430 --> 00:22:03.480
sasama ako!

00:22:03.480 --> 00:22:04.150
Pakiusap.

00:22:04.600 --> 00:22:05.840
Pagkatapos mo, ginoo.

00:22:12.940 --> 00:22:21.220
[Chunyun House]

00:23:07.550 --> 00:23:07.930
Dito.

00:23:13.430 --> 00:23:15.000
Ito ay talagang freeloading.

00:23:19.600 --> 00:23:20.600
Hindi sapat na malambot?

00:23:21.390 --> 00:23:22.190
Sapat na malambot.

00:23:24.880 --> 00:23:25.880
Nandito na si Song Jingye.

00:23:25.880 --> 00:23:27.270
Nasa likod siya, sa kwarto ng kapatid ko.

00:23:36.720 --> 00:23:37.220
Talunin ito!

00:23:39.240 --> 00:23:39.760
umalis ka na!

00:23:48.500 --> 00:23:51.940
[Qin Shi]

00:23:57.790 --> 00:23:58.600
Yingying.

00:23:59.640 --> 00:24:00.910
Huwag kang mag-abala.

00:24:01.760 --> 00:24:02.960
Dapat mong malaman,

00:24:04.030 --> 00:24:06.720
Hindi ako nandito para sa tsaa.

00:24:09.640 --> 00:24:10.760
Naiintindihan ni Yingying.

00:24:11.880 --> 00:24:14.000
Ngunit ito ay hindi maliit na bagay.

00:24:15.260 --> 00:24:16.800
Sana Chairman Song

00:24:16.880 --> 00:24:18.720
maaaring bigyan ng panahon si Yingying para makapag-isip.

00:24:23.640 --> 00:24:24.600
Pwede ba

00:24:25.120 --> 00:24:28.080
na hindi ako nagpakita ng sapat na sinseridad?

00:24:34.080 --> 00:24:36.310
Ang mga pumupunta rito ay pinahahalagahan ang kagandahan.

00:24:36.510 --> 00:24:38.840
Dapat nilang malaman na ang sapilitang pag-ibig ay hindi matamis.

00:24:39.310 --> 00:24:41.240
Mukhang masyadong naiinip ang bisitang ito.

00:24:41.880 --> 00:24:43.080
sino ka ba

00:24:43.960 --> 00:24:45.030
Bakit pumapasok?

00:24:45.880 --> 00:24:46.880
Kung naririto si Chairman Song,

00:24:46.880 --> 00:24:47.910
tapos kaya natin.

00:24:49.310 --> 00:24:50.150
Yingying.

00:24:50.760 --> 00:24:52.790
Isipin mo ang sinabi ko.

00:24:53.240 --> 00:24:54.190
alis muna ako.

00:24:56.760 --> 00:24:57.480
ate.

00:24:57.480 --> 00:24:58.670
Chairman Song, mangyaring manatili.

00:25:01.030 --> 00:25:02.360
nakita na kita dati.

00:25:02.640 --> 00:25:04.640
Ikaw ang nag-solve ng water poison issue.

00:25:04.790 --> 00:25:05.600
ako yun.

00:25:06.360 --> 00:25:08.840
Maaari ba akong makipag-usap kay Chairman Song mag-isa?

00:25:08.840 --> 00:25:10.120
Tinulungan mo ang Ma Gang,

00:25:11.030 --> 00:25:13.120
na nangangahulugan na ikaw ay laban sa Jibei Chamber of Commerce.

00:25:13.670 --> 00:25:15.240
Wala akong nakikitang pag-uusapan.

00:25:15.310 --> 00:25:17.030
Ipinadala ako ng aking ama para sa iyo.

00:25:17.880 --> 00:25:18.670
Ang tatay mo?

00:25:19.150 --> 00:25:20.080
Ang pangalan ko ay Fu Sheng.

00:25:20.640 --> 00:25:21.430
Ang iyong ama ay...

00:25:23.840 --> 00:25:24.760
Manggagamot Fu.

00:25:33.220 --> 00:25:36.980
[Chunyun House]

00:25:39.640 --> 00:25:40.640
Nakakita ka na ba ng mangangalakal

00:25:40.640 --> 00:25:41.270
umalis dito?

00:25:47.120 --> 00:25:47.790
Walang kwenta.

00:25:50.300 --> 00:25:53.380
[Chunyun House]

00:25:57.640 --> 00:26:00.640
Salamat sa iyong tulong ngayon, batang bayani.

00:26:01.270 --> 00:26:02.030
Huwag mag-alala.

00:26:04.640 --> 00:26:05.430
Hindi ko inaasahan

00:26:05.670 --> 00:26:07.240
ikaw ang maging top courtesan ng Chunyun House.

00:26:08.150 --> 00:26:09.640
Mga pakulo ko kanina

00:26:09.790 --> 00:26:10.670
napatawa ka siguro.

00:26:12.120 --> 00:26:13.510
Huwag mag-alala, batang bayani.

00:26:14.240 --> 00:26:16.310
Lagi kang iniistorbo ni Song Jingye.

00:26:17.080 --> 00:26:18.150
Sinusubukan ba niya

00:26:18.470 --> 00:26:19.840
gawin kang asawa niya?

00:26:22.190 --> 00:26:23.670
Aakyat na ako sa stage.

00:26:24.320 --> 00:26:25.080
Batang bayani,

00:26:25.430 --> 00:26:27.470
Paano kung maghanap ako ng ibang babae na makakasama mo?

00:26:28.080 --> 00:26:28.840
Hindi na kailangan.

00:26:29.320 --> 00:26:30.150
Huwag kang mag-abala.

00:26:30.840 --> 00:26:33.150
Hihintayin ko na lang dito si Fu Sheng.

00:26:48.360 --> 00:26:48.990
Hindi masama.

00:26:50.080 --> 00:26:51.750
Dapat yung binigay ko sa kanya.

00:26:53.950 --> 00:26:55.520
Itong Bird Jade Plate,

00:26:56.040 --> 00:26:57.230
regalo mo ba sa tatay ko?

00:27:01.190 --> 00:27:02.390
Sinabi sa akin ng aking ama

00:27:03.840 --> 00:27:05.280
itong Bird Jade Plate,

00:27:05.600 --> 00:27:08.150
dapat ipares sa Ulap, Tubig, at Bundok

00:27:08.430 --> 00:27:09.470
tatlong piraso ng jade.

00:27:10.080 --> 00:27:11.710
Saka lamang nito maa-unlock ang Treasure of the Sealed Book.

00:27:12.430 --> 00:27:14.670
Nasa kamay mo rin daw ang hugis Ulap na Jade.

00:27:15.430 --> 00:27:16.190
Chairman Song,

00:27:17.230 --> 00:27:18.560
pwede mo bang sabihin sa akin

